.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Crouser\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not many men can say they have taken on that kind of stature.\\\"\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ato Boldon on women's 100m winner Julien Alfred's home country of Saint Lucia: \\\"There is going to be an island-wide motorcade the likes of which has never been seen in Saint Lucia...\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3197, \"end\": 3208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7747405755814065e-11, \"text\": \"Saint Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}, {\"begin\": 3299, \"end\": 3310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7747405755814065e-11, \"text\": \"Saint Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was no contest.\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not close.\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She looked the best through the rounds and she dominated this Olympic final.\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Saint Lucia, your first medal in the Olympics is gold, brought to you byJulien Alfred...Fewer than 200,000 people.\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3430, \"end\": 3441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7747405755814065e-11, \"text\": \"Saint Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"238 square miles - that's the size of Tucson, Arizona.\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3583, \"end\": 3598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.9702355067530135, \"rank\": 0.03067759635661338, \"text\": \"Tucson, Arizona\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_Stadium\"}, {\"begin\": 3583, \"end\": 3598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.9702355067530135, \"rank\": 0.03067759635661338, \"text\": \"Tucson, Arizona\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_Stadium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And yet somehow, the Caribbean dominance of this event continues.\\\"\", \"from\": 3600, \"to\": 3666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Leigh Diffey on the women's 100m final: \\\"It's a great night for Team USA - it's an exceptional night for the small Caribbean nation of Saint Lucia.\\\"\", \"from\": 3668, \"to\": 3816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3668, \"end\": 3680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leigh_Diffey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leigh Diffey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leigh_Diffey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leigh_Diffey\"}, {\"begin\": 3803, \"end\": 3814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7747405755814065e-11, \"text\": \"Saint Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sanya Richards-Ross on Femke Bol anchoring the Netherlands to a gold medal in the mixed 4x400m relay: \\\"Can you imagine the confidence she's going to have going into the 400m hurdles?\", \"from\": 3818, \"to\": 4000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3841, \"end\": 3850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Femke_Bol\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Femke Bol\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Femke_Bol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Femke_Bol\"}, {\"begin\": 3865, \"end\": 3876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999837014457083, \"rank\": 1.5265027308337338e-05, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the kind of start you want to have to your Olympics when you are about to face one of the greatest athletes that will be in the building,Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone.\\\"\", \"from\": 4001, \"to\": 4172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hardee on the difficulty of the decathlon: \\\"The decathlon is, by far, the hardest event in track & field, and this moment right here [pole vault] is the most difficult discipline to master.\", \"from\": 4174, \"to\": 4363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are physically fatigued, weather is beating down on you, you are fatigued mentally.\", \"from\": 4364, \"to\": 4451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This event just grinds on you.\\\"\", \"from\": 4452, \"to\": 4483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SWIMMING  Dan Hicks on Katie Ledecky after winning the women's 800m freestyle for the fourth consecutive Olympics:\\\"Every single time Ledecky gets in the pool, history is at stake, and pretty much every time, Ledecky takes care of it.\\\"\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4495, \"end\": 4504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Hicks_(singer)\", \"score\": 0.7661863309397541, \"rank\": 0.2941348117887413, \"text\": \"Dan Hicks\", \"types\"