ch an emotional time\\u2026 these guys are playing for millions and millions of dollars (on a weekly basis.\", \"from\": 5993, \"to\": 6195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is different.\", \"from\": 6196, \"to\": 6214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just different.\", \"from\": 6215, \"to\": 6235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It just means something more.\\\"\", \"from\": 6236, \"to\": 6266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TENNIS  American doubles player Rajeev Ram on the emotions of coming up just short: \\\"You play your heart out for your country in these moments, and we were so close\\u2026 it's wonderful to win a silver\\u2026but today was tough.\\\"\", \"from\": 6268, \"to\": 6486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6300, \"end\": 6310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rajeev Ram\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajeev_Ram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WOMEN'S SOCCER  Jon Champion on Trinity Rodman's goal in the 105th minute: \\\"A special moment!\", \"from\": 6488, \"to\": 6581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Twenty-two-year-old Trinity Rodman - take a bow!\\\"\", \"from\": 6582, \"to\": 6631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Julie Foudy on the firepower for the U.S.: \\\"It is a sign of respect for this United States team when you see teams unwilling to come out and open up against them.\", \"from\": 6633, \"to\": 6795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6633, \"end\": 6644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julie_Foudy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Julie Foudy\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julie_Foudy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julie_Foudy\"}, {\"begin\": 6710, \"end\": 6723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Un